description:
Do you fancy meeting other singles in an informal, casual setting? Are you a young professional who often does not have the time or energy to deal with matchmaking and online dating sites? Then you are in the right place. LetsMeet offers you a platform to meet a variety of singles through different networking events.


Hast du Lust auf ein ungezwungenes, lockeres Zusammentreffen mit anderen Singles? Bist du berufstätig und hast du oft keine Zeit und keine Energie dich mit Verkupplungen und Online-Dating Seiten auseinanderzusetzen? Dann bist du hier genau richtig. LetsMeet ermöglicht es dir durch unterschiedliche Networking Events verschiedenste Singles unverbindlich zu treffen. An wen richten wir uns? Unsere Afterwork-Events richten sich an Singles und Nicht-Singles und Freunde und Freunde von Freunden, die Singles mitbringen. Nimm an einem unserer Afterwork-Events teil und packe die Gelegenheit um in interessanter Gesellschaft den Abend ausklingen zu lassen. Du wirst neue Leute kennenlernen und wer weiss, vielleicht wirst du oder deine Single-Freunde eine vielversprechende Bekanntschaft machen. Wir würden uns freuen dich, deine Single-Freunde und Nicht-Single-Freunde sehr bald persönlich kennenzulernen. www.letsmeet.ch

category.name: singles
description:
Perhaps you are the only person in your group of friends without a girl/boyfriend? Maybe it bothers you to continuously "third wheel" when out with your friends and their partners? Or could it be that you are taking a break from swiping right and left on your mobile phone?

DearHunt is a group aimed at all Single men & women in and around the Zurich area interested in meeting new friends, partners, and companions. Whether you are a local, a newcomer, or a visitor to Zurich - the purpose of this group is to bring together like-minded individuals face-to-face, by meeting & mingling at monthly events; events include after-work drinks and shared-interest based activities. 

DearHunt encourages its members to build and grow Zurich's singles community by attending events accompanied by another single of the opposite sex. This provides a larger probability of lasting connections for individuals with whom you share a purpose, goal, interest, or identity. Additionally, these face-to-face introductions, made by singles for singles, stimulate shared community-building. 

Looking forward to meeting you!

ⓘ This Meetup platform is not a dating service or dating clinic. I do not claim to be a date coach, matchmaker or otherwise.

description:
"Ein Treffen für Singles, die gerne neue Leute kennenlernen und plus-minus um die 50ig sind. Ich starte die Gruppe da der Altersunterschied an anderen Treffen sehr spürbar ist. Natürlich ist das ähnliche Alter keine Garantie für Freund- und Frau-schaften und doch... könnte es doch sein - oder?

Ziel des Treffens könnte die Planung eines gemeinsamen Unternehmens sein: Besuch Ausstellung/Musuem, Kino, Konzert, Velo fahren, Wandern, Picknick  u.ä.m - Feuer im Winter draussen grillen (mein Favorit)....Freue mich Dich / Euch kennenzulernen.

A meeting for singles who like to get to know new people in there age. Maybe we will fix a date to do something together. Cinema, concerts or a nice winter-grill in the woods (that's my favorit). Looking forward to getting to know you.

category.name: singles
description:
Finding the right man and keeping him can be an arduous task for many of us, but there are secrets of dating and relationships we should all know. This group is for women who would like to find out exactly what does go on in a man's mind. More than just dating and relationship advice, we will be looking at how we think can actually work against us in many instances, as well as how we can increase our confidence levels. Of course many women like to think they can attract any guy, but it's not any guy we are after, it's the right guy, and unfortunately the more we are attracted the more we can sometimes self sabotage.

This group is for this who want to know more about a subject that we all like to think we are good at, but our results may differ. It's not just about dating, it's about knowing the inside track on how to keep the right man interested in the long term.

Female empowerment is something we all aspire to enjoy, so why not join the group and we will arrange some top quality speakers to tell us how.
name: HOW TO GET THAT GUY AND KEEP HIM

category.name: singles
description: How to be single - es musste ein kurzer Meetupgruppenname her - Deine Freunde heiraten, bekommen Kinder und sind mit Päärliabenden beschäftigt und du willst einfach nur auf den Putz hauen und dich mit Gleichgesinnten über das Universum und die Welt austauschen...Dann bist du hier genau richtig! Das Motto sagt schon viel. Bern ist zwar klein aber auch hier lässt es sich leben und auf den Putz hauen ;) Bist du auch um die Dreissig, Single und suchst Gleichgesinnte? Dann let`s go! Dieses Meet up ist nicht als Verkupplungs- oder Datingplattform gedacht sondern als Gruppe bei der sich Singles treffen, die noch nicht gerade Heiraten oder Kinder haben möchten, sondern beruflich neue Perspektiven anstreben, das Nachtleben geniessen wollen, gute Gespräche und den Austausch mit Gleichgesinnten suchen und zusammen eventuell den einen oder anderen Ausflug machen wollen.
name: How to Be Single Bern
organizer.name: Simone

category.name: singles
description:
Do you fancy meeting other singles in an informal, casual setting? Are you a young professional who often does not have the time or energy to deal with matchmaking and online dating sites? Then you are in the right place. LetsMeet offers you a platform to meet a variety of singles through different networking events.


Hast du Lust auf ein ungezwungenes, lockeres Zusammentreffen mit anderen Singles? Bist du berufstätig und hast du oft keine Zeit und keine Energie dich mit Verkupplungen und Online-Dating Seiten auseinanderzusetzen? Dann bist du hier genau richtig. LetsMeet ermöglicht es dir durch unterschiedliche Networking Events verschiedenste Singles unverbindlich zu treffen. An wen richten wir uns? Unsere Afterwork-Events richten sich an Singles und Nicht-Singles und Freunde und Freunde von Freunden, die Singles mitbringen. Nimm an einem unserer Afterwork-Events teil und packe die Gelegenheit um in interessanter Gesellschaft den Abend ausklingen zu lassen. Du wirst neue Leute kennenlernen und wer weiss, vielleicht wirst du oder deine Single-Freunde eine vielversprechende Bekanntschaft machen. Wir würden uns freuen dich, deine Single-Freunde und Nicht-Single-Freunde sehr bald persönlich kennenzulernen. www.letsmeet.ch
name: LetsMeet - Single Network & Events

category.name: singles
description:
Perhaps you are the only person in your group of friends without a girl/boyfriend? Maybe it bothers you to continuously "third wheel" when out with your friends and their partners? Or could it be that you are taking a break from swiping right and left on your mobile phone?

DearHunt is a group aimed at all Single men & women in and around the Zurich area interested in meeting new friends, partners, and companions. Whether you are a local, a newcomer, or a visitor to Zurich - the purpose of this group is to bring together like-minded individuals face-to-face, by meeting & mingling at monthly events; events include after-work drinks and shared-interest based activities. 

DearHunt encourages its members to build and grow Zurich's singles community by attending events accompanied by another single of the opposite sex. This provides a larger probability of lasting connections for individuals with whom you share a purpose, goal, interest, or identity. Additionally, these face-to-face introductions, made by singles for singles, stimulate shared community-building. 

Looking forward to meeting you!

ⓘ This Meetup platform is not a dating service or dating clinic. I do not claim to be a date coach, matchmaker or otherwise.

"Ein Treffen für Singles, die gerne neue Leute kennenlernen und plus-minus um die 50ig sind. Ich starte die Gruppe da der Altersunterschied an anderen Treffen sehr spürbar ist. Natürlich ist das ähnliche Alter keine Garantie für Freund- und Frau-schaften und doch... könnte es doch sein - oder?

Sich vorstellen, plaudern, auch Gesprächspausen zulassen ... Ziel des Treffens könnte die Planung eines gemeinsamen Unternehmens sein: Besuch Ausstellung/Musuem, Kino, Konzert, Velo fahren, Wandern, Picknick  u.ä.m - Feuer im Winter draussen grillen (mein Favorit)....Freue mich Dich / Euch kennenzulernen.

A meeting for singles who like to get to know new people in there age. Maybe we will fix a date to do something together. Cinema, concerts or a nice winter-grill in the woods (that's my favorit). Looking forward to getting to know you.
name: Zürich Singles, +/- 50 Meetup
organizer.name: katharina

category.name: singles
description:
Finding the right man and keeping him can be an arduous task for many of us, but there are secrets of dating and relationships we should all know. This group is for women who would like to find out exactly what does go on in a man's mind. More than just dating and relationship advice, we will be looking at how we think can actually work against us in many instances, as well as how we can increase our confidence levels. Of course many women like to think they can attract any guy, but it's not any guy we are after, it's the right guy, and unfortunately the more we are attracted the more we can sometimes self sabotage.

This group is for this who want to know more about a subject that we all like to think we are good at, but our results may differ. It's not just about dating, it's about knowing the inside track on how to keep the right man interested in the long term.

Female empowerment is something we all aspire to enjoy, so why not join the group and we will arrange some top quality speakers to tell us how.
name: HOW TO GET THAT GUY AND KEEP HIM

category.name: singles
description:
Do you fancy meeting other singles in an informal, casual setting? Are you a young professional who often does not have the time or energy to deal with matchmaking and online dating sites? Then you are in the right place. LetsMeet offers you a platform to meet a variety of singles through different networking events.


Hast du Lust auf ein ungezwungenes, lockeres Zusammentreffen mit anderen Singles? Bist du berufstätig und hast du oft keine Zeit und keine Energie dich mit Verkupplungen und Online-Dating Seiten auseinanderzusetzen? Dann bist du hier genau richtig. LetsMeet ermöglicht es dir durch unterschiedliche Networking Events verschiedenste Singles unverbindlich zu treffen. An wen richten wir uns? Unsere Afterwork-Events richten sich an Singles und Nicht-Singles und Freunde und Freunde von Freunden, die Singles mitbringen. Nimm an einem unserer Afterwork-Events teil und packe die Gelegenheit um in interessanter Gesellschaft den Abend ausklingen zu lassen. Du wirst neue Leute kennenlernen und wer weiss, vielleicht wirst du oder deine Single-Freunde eine vielversprechende Bekanntschaft machen. Wir würden uns freuen dich, deine Single-Freunde und Nicht-Single-Freunde sehr bald persönlich kennenzulernen. www.letsmeet.ch
name: LetsMeet - Single Network & Events
organizer.name: Gil

category.name: singles
description:
Perhaps you are the only person in your group of friends without a girl/boyfriend? Maybe it bothers you to continuously "third wheel" when out with your friends and their partners? Or could it be that you are taking a break from swiping right and left on your mobile phone?

DearHunt is a group aimed at all Single men & women in and around the Zurich area interested in meeting new friends, partners, and companions. Whether you are a local, a newcomer, or a visitor to Zurich - the purpose of this group is to bring together like-minded individuals face-to-face, by meeting & mingling at monthly events; events include after-work drinks and shared-interest based activities. 

DearHunt encourages its members to build and grow Zurich's singles community by attending events accompanied by another single of the opposite sex. This provides a larger probability of lasting connections for individuals with whom you share a purpose, goal, interest, or identity. Additionally, these face-to-face introductions, made by singles for singles, stimulate shared community-building. 

Looking forward to meeting you!

ⓘ This Meetup platform is not a dating service or dating clinic. I do not claim to be a date coach, matchmaker or otherwise.
name: DearHunt: Zurich's Singles Community

description: How to be single - es musste ein kurzer Meetupgruppenname her - Deine Freunde heiraten, bekommen Kinder und sind mit Päärliabenden beschäftigt und du willst einfach nur auf den Putz hauen und dich mit Gleichgesinnten über das Universum und die Welt austauschen...Dann bist du hier genau richtig! Das Motto sagt schon viel. Bern ist zwar klein aber auch hier lässt es sich leben und auf den Putz hauen ;) Bist du auch um die Dreissig, Single und suchst Gleichgesinnte? Dann let`s go! Dieses Meet up ist nicht als Verkupplungs- oder Datingplattform gedacht sondern als Gruppe bei der sich Singles treffen, die noch nicht gerade Heiraten oder Kinder haben möchten, sondern beruflich neue Perspektiven anstreben, das Nachtleben geniessen wollen, gute Gespräche und den Austausch mit Gleichgesinnten suchen und zusammen eventuell den einen oder anderen Ausflug machen wollen.
name: How to Be Single Bern

category.name: singles
description:
Perhaps you are the only person in your group of friends without a girl/boyfriend? Maybe it bothers you to continuously "third wheel" when out with your friends and their partners? Or could it be that you are taking a break from swiping right and left on your mobile phone?

DearHunt is a group aimed at all Single men & women in and around the Zurich area interested in meeting new friends, partners, and companions. Whether you are a local, a newcomer, or a visitor to Zurich - the purpose of this group is to bring together like-minded individuals face-to-face, by meeting & mingling at monthly events; events include after-work drinks and shared-interest based activities. 

DearHunt encourages its members to build and grow Zurich's singles community by attending events accompanied by another single of the opposite sex. This provides a larger probability of lasting connections for individuals with whom you share a purpose, goal, interest, or identity. Additionally, these face-to-face introductions, made by singles for singles, stimulate shared community-building. 

Looking forward to meeting you!

ⓘ This Meetup platform is not a dating service or dating clinic. I do not claim to be a date coach, matchmaker or otherwise.

category.name: singles
description:
"Ein Treffen für Singles, die gerne neue Leute kennenlernen und plus-minus um die 50ig sind. Ich starte die Gruppe da der Altersunterschied an anderen Treffen sehr spürbar ist. Natürlich ist das ähnliche Alter keine Garantie für Freund- und Frau-schaften und doch... könnte es doch sein - oder?

Sich vorstellen, plaudern, auch Gesprächspausen zulassen ... Ziel des Treffens könnte die Planung eines gemeinsamen Unternehmens sein: Besuch Ausstellung/Musuem, Kino, Konzert, Velo fahren, Wandern, Picknick  u.ä.m - Feuer im Winter draussen grillen (mein Favorit)....Freue mich Dich / Euch kennenzulernen.

A meeting for singles who like to get to know new people in there age. Maybe we will fix a date to do something together. Cinema, concerts or a nice winter-grill in the woods (that's my favorit). Looking forward to getting to know you.
name: Zürich Singles, +/- 50 Meetup

category.name: singles
description:
Finding the right man and keeping him can be an arduous task for many of us, but there are secrets of dating and relationships we should all know. This group is for women who would like to find out exactly what does go on in a man's mind. More than just dating and relationship advice, we will be looking at how we think can actually work against us in many instances, as well as how we can increase our confidence levels. Of course many women like to think they can attract any guy, but it's not any guy we are after, it's the right guy, and unfortunately the more we are attracted the more we can sometimes self sabotage.

This group is for this who want to know more about a subject that we all like to think we are good at, but our results may differ. It's not just about dating, it's about knowing the inside track on how to keep the right man interested in the long term.

Female empowerment is something we all aspire to enjoy, so why not join the group and we will arrange some top quality speakers to tell us how.
name: HOW TO GET THAT GUY AND KEEP HIM

category.name: singles
description:
Do you fancy meeting other singles in an informal, casual setting? Are you a young professional who often does not have the time or energy to deal with matchmaking and online dating sites? Then you are in the right place. LetsMeet offers you a platform to meet a variety of singles through different networking events.


Hast du Lust auf ein ungezwungenes, lockeres Zusammentreffen mit anderen Singles? Bist du berufstätig und hast du oft keine Zeit und keine Energie dich mit Verkupplungen und Online-Dating Seiten auseinanderzusetzen? Dann bist du hier genau richtig. LetsMeet ermöglicht es dir durch unterschiedliche Networking Events verschiedenste Singles unverbindlich zu treffen. An wen richten wir uns? Unsere Afterwork-Events richten sich an Singles und Nicht-Singles und Freunde und Freunde von Freunden, die Singles mitbringen. Nimm an einem unserer Afterwork-Events teil und packe die Gelegenheit um in interessanter Gesellschaft den Abend ausklingen zu lassen. Du wirst neue Leute kennenlernen und wer weiss, vielleicht wirst du oder deine Single-Freunde eine vielversprechende Bekanntschaft machen. Wir würden uns freuen dich, deine Single-Freunde und Nicht-Single-Freunde sehr bald persönlich kennenzulernen. www.letsmeet.ch

category.name: singles
description:
Do you fancy meeting other singles in an informal, casual setting? Are you a young professional who often does not have the time or energy to deal with matchmaking and online dating sites? Then you are in the right place. LetsMeet offers you a platform to meet a variety of singles through different networking events.


Hast du Lust auf ein ungezwungenes, lockeres Zusammentreffen mit anderen Singles? Bist du berufstätig und hast du oft keine Zeit und keine Energie dich mit Verkupplungen und Online-Dating Seiten auseinanderzusetzen? Dann bist du hier genau richtig. LetsMeet ermöglicht es dir durch unterschiedliche Networking Events verschiedenste Singles unverbindlich zu treffen. An wen richten wir uns? Unsere Afterwork-Events richten sich an Singles und Nicht-Singles und Freunde und Freunde von Freunden, die Singles mitbringen. Nimm an einem unserer Afterwork-Events teil und packe die Gelegenheit um in interessanter Gesellschaft den Abend ausklingen zu lassen. Du wirst neue Leute kennenlernen und wer weiss, vielleicht wirst du oder deine Single-Freunde eine vielversprechende Bekanntschaft machen. Wir würden uns freuen dich, deine Single-Freunde und Nicht-Single-Freunde sehr bald persönlich kennenzulernen. www.letsmeet.ch
name: LetsMeet - Single Network & Events

category.name: singles
description:
Perhaps you are the only person in your group of friends without a girl/boyfriend? Maybe it bothers you to continuously "third wheel" when out with your friends and their partners? Or could it be that you are taking a break from swiping right and left on your mobile phone?

DearHunt is a group aimed at all Single men & women in and around the Zurich area interested in meeting new friends, partners, and companions. Whether you are a local, a newcomer, or a visitor to Zurich - the purpose of this group is to bring together like-minded individuals face-to-face, by meeting & mingling at monthly events; events include after-work drinks and shared-interest based activities. 

DearHunt encourages its members to build and grow Zurich's singles community by attending events accompanied by another single of the opposite sex. This provides a larger probability of lasting connections for individuals with whom you share a purpose, goal, interest, or identity. Additionally, these face-to-face introductions, made by singles for singles, stimulate shared community-building. 

Looking forward to meeting you!

ⓘ This Meetup platform is not a dating service or dating clinic. I do not claim to be a date coach, matchmaker or otherwise.

category.name: singles
description:
"Ein Treffen für Singles, die gerne neue Leute kennenlernen und plus-minus um die 50ig sind. Ich starte die Gruppe da der Altersunterschied an anderen Treffen sehr spürbar ist. Natürlich ist das ähnliche Alter keine Garantie für Freund- und Frau-schaften und doch... könnte es doch sein - oder?

Sich vorstellen, plaudern, auch Gesprächspausen zulassen ... Ziel des Treffens könnte die Planung eines gemeinsamen Unternehmens sein: Besuch Ausstellung/Musuem, Kino, Konzert, Velo fahren, Wandern, Picknick  u.ä.m - Feuer im Winter draussen grillen (mein Favorit)....Freue mich Dich / Euch kennenzulernen.

A meeting for singles who like to get to know new people in there age. Maybe we will fix a date to do something together. Cinema, concerts or a nice winter-grill in the woods (that's my favorit). Looking forward to getting to know you.
name: Zürich Singles, +/- 50 Meetup

category.name: singles
description:
Finding the right man and keeping him can be an arduous task for many of us, but there are secrets of dating and relationships we should all know. This group is for women who would like to find out exactly what does go on in a man's mind. More than just dating and relationship advice, we will be looking at how we think can actually work against us in many instances, as well as how we can increase our confidence levels. Of course many women like to think they can attract any guy, but it's not any guy we are after, it's the right guy, and unfortunately the more we are attracted the more we can sometimes self sabotage.

This group is for this who want to know more about a subject that we all like to think we are good at, but our results may differ. It's not just about dating, it's about knowing the inside track on how to keep the right man interested in the long term.

Female empowerment is something we all aspire to enjoy, so why not join the group and we will arrange some top quality speakers to tell us how.
name: HOW TO GET THAT GUY AND KEEP HIM

category.name: singles
description:
Do you fancy meeting other singles in an informal, casual setting? Are you a young professional who often does not have the time or energy to deal with matchmaking and online dating sites? Then you are in the right place. LetsMeet offers you a platform to meet a variety of singles through different networking events.


Hast du Lust auf ein ungezwungenes, lockeres Zusammentreffen mit anderen Singles? Bist du berufstätig und hast du oft keine Zeit und keine Energie dich mit Verkupplungen und Online-Dating Seiten auseinanderzusetzen? Dann bist du hier genau richtig. LetsMeet ermöglicht es dir durch unterschiedliche Networking Events verschiedenste Singles unverbindlich zu treffen. An wen richten wir uns? Unsere Afterwork-Events richten sich an Singles und Nicht-Singles und Freunde und Freunde von Freunden, die Singles mitbringen. Nimm an einem unserer Afterwork-Events teil und packe die Gelegenheit um in interessanter Gesellschaft den Abend ausklingen zu lassen. Du wirst neue Leute kennenlernen und wer weiss, vielleicht wirst du oder deine Single-Freunde eine vielversprechende Bekanntschaft machen. Wir würden uns freuen dich, deine Single-Freunde und Nicht-Single-Freunde sehr bald persönlich kennenzulernen. www.letsmeet.ch
name: LetsMeet - Single Network & Events

category.name: singles
description:
Perhaps you are the only person in your group of friends without a girl/boyfriend? Maybe it bothers you to continuously "third wheel" when out with your friends and their partners? Or could it be that you are taking a break from swiping right and left on your mobile phone?

DearHunt is a group aimed at all Single men & women in and around the Zurich area interested in meeting new friends, partners, and companions. Whether you are a local, a newcomer, or a visitor to Zurich - the purpose of this group is to bring together like-minded individuals face-to-face, by meeting & mingling at monthly events; events include after-work drinks and shared-interest based activities. 

DearHunt encourages its members to build and grow Zurich's singles community by attending events accompanied by another single of the opposite sex. This provides a larger probability of lasting connections for individuals with whom you share a purpose, goal, interest, or identity. Additionally, these face-to-face introductions, made by singles for singles, stimulate shared community-building. 

Looking forward to meeting you!

ⓘ This Meetup platform is not a dating service or dating clinic. I do not claim to be a date coach, matchmaker or otherwise.
name: DearHunt: Zurich's Singles Community

Then you are in the right place. LetsMeet offers you a platform to meet a variety of singles through different networking events.


Hast du Lust auf ein ungezwungenes, lockeres Zusammentreffen mit anderen Singles? Bist du berufstätig und hast du oft keine Zeit und keine Energie dich mit Verkupplungen und Online-Dating Seiten auseinanderzusetzen? Dann bist du hier genau richtig. LetsMeet ermöglicht es dir durch unterschiedliche Networking Events verschiedenste Singles unverbindlich zu treffen. An wen richten wir uns? Unsere Afterwork-Events richten sich an Singles und Nicht-Singles und Freunde und Freunde von Freunden, die Singles mitbringen. Nimm an einem unserer Afterwork-Events teil und packe die Gelegenheit um in interessanter Gesellschaft den Abend ausklingen zu lassen. Du wirst neue Leute kennenlernen und wer weiss, vielleicht wirst du oder deine Single-Freunde eine vielversprechende Bekanntschaft machen. Wir würden uns freuen dich, deine Single-Freunde und Nicht-Single-Freunde sehr bald persönlich kennenzulernen. www.letsmeet.ch
name: LetsMeet - Single Network & Events

category.name: singles
description:
Perhaps you are the only person in your group of friends without a girl/boyfriend? Maybe it bothers you to continuously "third wheel" when out with your friends and their partners? Or could it be that you are taking a break from swiping right and left on your mobile phone?

DearHunt is a group aimed at all Single men & women in and around the Zurich area interested in meeting new friends, partners, and companions. Whether you are a local, a newcomer, or a visitor to Zurich - the purpose of this group is to bring together like-minded individuals face-to-face, by meeting & mingling at monthly events; events include after-work drinks and shared-interest based activities. 

DearHunt encourages its members to build and grow Zurich's singles community by attending events accompanied by another single of the opposite sex. This provides a larger probability of lasting connections for individuals with whom you share a purpose, goal, interest, or identity. Additionally, these face-to-face introductions, made by singles for singles, stimulate shared community-building. 

Looking forward to meeting you!

ⓘ This Meetup platform is not a dating service or dating clinic. I do not claim to be a date coach, matchmaker or otherwise.

description:
"Ein Treffen für Singles, die gerne neue Leute kennenlernen und plus-minus um die 50ig sind. Ich starte die Gruppe da der Altersunterschied an anderen Treffen sehr spürbar ist. Natürlich ist das ähnliche Alter keine Garantie für Freund- und Frau-schaften und doch... könnte es doch sein - oder?

Sich vorstellen, plaudern, auch Gesprächspausen zulassen ... Ziel des Treffens könnte die Planung eines gemeinsamen Unternehmens sein: Besuch Ausstellung/Musuem, Kino, Konzert, Velo fahren, Wandern, Picknick  u.ä.m - Feuer im Winter draussen grillen (mein Favorit)....Freue mich Dich / Euch kennenzulernen.

A meeting for singles who like to get to know new people in there age. Maybe we will fix a date to do something together. Cinema, concerts or a nice winter-grill in the woods (that's my favorit). Looking forward to getting to know you.
name: Zürich Singles, +/- 50 Meetup

category.name: singles
description:
Finding the right man and keeping him can be an arduous task for many of us, but there are secrets of dating and relationships we should all know. This group is for women who would like to find out exactly what does go on in a man's mind. More than just dating and relationship advice, we will be looking at how we think can actually work against us in many instances, as well as how we can increase our confidence levels. Of course many women like to think they can attract any guy, but it's not any guy we are after, it's the right guy, and unfortunately the more we are attracted the more we can sometimes self sabotage.

This group is for this who want to know more about a subject that we all like to think we are good at, but our results may differ. It's not just about dating, it's about knowing the inside track on how to keep the right man interested in the long term.

Female empowerment is something we all aspire to enjoy, so why not join the group and we will arrange some top quality speakers to tell us how.
name: HOW TO GET THAT GUY AND KEEP HIM

description:

DearHunt is a group aimed at all Single men & women in and around the Zurich area interested in meeting new friends, partners, and companions. Whether you are a local, a newcomer, or a visitor to Zurich - the purpose of this group is to bring together like-minded individuals face-to-face, by meeting & mingling at monthly events; events include after-work drinks and shared-interest based activities.

description:

A meeting for singles who like to get to know new people in there age. Maybe we will fix a date to do something together. Cinema, concerts or a nice winter-grill in the woods (that's my favorit). Looking forward to getting to know you.

category.name: singles
description:
Finding the right man and keeping him can be an arduous task for many of us, but there are secrets of dating and relationships we should all know. This group is for women who would like to find out exactly what does go on in a man's mind. More than just dating and relationship advice, we will be looking at how we think can actually work against us in many instances, as well as how we can increase our confidence levels. Of course many women like to think they can attract any guy, but it's not any guy we are after, it's the right guy, and unfortunately the more we are attracted the more we can sometimes self sabotage.

This group is for this who want to know more about a subject that we all like to think we are good at, but our results may differ. It's not just about dating, it's about knowing the inside track on how to keep the right man interested in the long term.

Female empowerment is something we all aspire to enjoy, so why not join the group and we will arrange some top quality speakers to tell us how.
name: HOW TO GET THAT GUY AND KEEP HIM

description: How to be single - es musste ein kurzer Meetupgruppenname her - Deine Freunde heiraten, bekommen Kinder und sind mit Päärliabenden beschäftigt und du willst einfach nur auf den Putz hauen und dich mit Gleichgesinnten über das Universum und die Welt austauschen...Dann bist du hier genau richtig! Das Motto sagt schon viel. Bern ist zwar klein aber auch hier lässt es sich leben und auf den Putz hauen ;) Bist du auch um die Dreissig, Single und suchst Gleichgesinnte? Dann let`s go! Dieses Meet up ist nicht als Verkupplungs- oder Datingplattform gedacht sondern als Gruppe bei der sich Singles treffen, die noch nicht gerade Heiraten oder Kinder haben möchten, sondern beruflich neue Perspektiven anstreben, das Nachtleben geniessen wollen, gute Gespräche und den Austausch mit Gleichgesinnten suchen und zusammen eventuell den einen oder anderen Ausflug machen wollen.
name: How to Be Single Bern

category.name: singles
description:
Finding the right man and keeping him can be an arduous task for many of us, but there are secrets of dating and relationships we should all know. This group is for women who would like to find out exactly what does go on in a man's mind. More than just dating and relationship advice, we will be looking at how we think can actually work against us in many instances, as well as how we can increase our confidence levels. Of course many women like to think they can attract any guy, but it's not any guy we are after, it's the right guy, and unfortunately the more we are attracted the more we can sometimes self sabotage.

This group is for this who want to know more about a subject that we all like to think we are good at, but our results may differ. It's not just about dating, it's about knowing the inside track on how to keep the right man interested in the long term.

Female empowerment is something we all aspire to enjoy, so why not join the group and we will arrange some top quality speakers to tell us how.
name: HOW TO GET THAT GUY AND KEEP HIM
